headline: New railroad debuts in Louisville, offering West Coast connections. Here's what we know
summary: Two major railroad companies have joined forces to launch a new freight line connecting Louisville to the West Coast. Here's what we know.

headline: New UP-NS Louisville intermodal hauling for GE Appliances
summary: GE Appliances has signed on to the new Union Pacific-Norfolk Southern domestic intermodal route serving key markets via west and southwest ports. The post New UP-NS Louisville intermodal hauling for GE Appliances appeared first on FreightWaves.
